```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>VEP's Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to VEP's Blog!</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a> |
        <a href="about.html">About</a> |
        <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <p>This is my awesome Y2K retro blog powered by MogBot!</p>
</body>
</html>
```

✅ **style.css**
```css
body {
    background-color: black;
    color: lime;
    font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
    text-align: center;
}
a {
    color: cyan;
}
```

